location.fullValue: The Wayne Plan, True Homes On Your Lot - Magnolia Greens

data.description: BIG PRICE REDUCTION!! This is an Estate Sale. We have contractor estimates in hand to do stress free renovations which will make this home feel BRAND NEW. Please inquire further. Welcome to the beautiful neighborhood of Waterford. You will immediately unwind and relax surrounded by the coastal development theme of waterfront villas and top of the line recreational amenities. This one story, brick home offers low maintenance living, water feature views and it's own fishing dock perfect for enjoying the outdoors or happy hour with friends. Inside has just been professional painted and cleaned offering a head start for new owners. You will appreciate the open floor plan, engineered floors in the living room, fireplace and stainless appliances. Be sure to check out the amazing pool area, tennis courts, playground and community facilities. Waterford is ideally located to all of Leland's shopping and restaurants yet only 10 Minutes to historic downtown Wilmington on the River, 30 minutes to Southport/Oak Island, 20-30 minutes to Wrightsville Beach. Motivated to sell.
